2. Can you tell me about your Current Project?

"In my recent project, I worked for Steelcase as a Power Apps Developer, 
where I developed internal business applications using Power Apps, Power Automate, Dataverse, and SharePoint.
The main objective of the project was to replace manual Excel-based processes with automated and centralized applications to improve efficiency and data accuracy.

I developed two major applications. 
The first was an Inventory Management Canvas App to track furniture stock across multiple warehouses.
It included features like search and filter, low-stock alerts, and role-based access control. 
The second was a Model-Driven Order Tracking application built on Dataverse to manage purchase orders and approvals. 
I also implemented approval workflows using Power Automate, automated notifications, handled security roles, and managed deployments. 
This project significantly reduced manual errors, improved tracking, and streamlined approval processes across departments."
